snippet: People who live along the rocky Galician coastline of Spain must fight poachers and dangerous conditions in the hunt for barnacles.
abstract: A Coruna Journal; people who live along the rocky Galician coastline of Spain must fight poachers and dangerous conditions in the hunt for gooseneck barnacles; in difficult economic times, fewer people can afford to buy these rare crustaceans.
lead_paragraph: People who live along the rocky Galician coastline of Spain must fight poachers and dangerous conditions in the hunt for barnacles.

headline.main: Scraping for Sea Delicacy, and a Meager Living
